(95676, @GROUP_ID+0, @ID+0, 'Throughout your trials, you have demonstrated strength, skill, and intellect-traits shared by the greatest of our vrykul kings. Now... you will face them in combat. Emerge victorious, and you may yet claim your prize!', 14, 0, 100, 0, 0, 54613, 100271, 'Odyn to Player'),
