(102600, @GROUP_ID+7, @ID+0, 'Both currents feed into the central chamber. Use the coils and switches to direct the currents and power all four seals in the central chamber!', 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 67428, 105575, 'Arcanist Valtrois to Player'),
